Name: NumberOfFills
Description: The total number of trades that filled

Name: NumberOfRejects
Description: The total number of trades that where rejected

Name: FillVolume
Description: Total volume of the trades that where filled

Name: RejectVolume
Description: Total volume of the trades that where rejected

Name: AvgTradeSizeUSD
Description: The average size in USD of a trade

Name: SpreadPaid
Description: Spread Paid (expressed $/m) - relative difference between price paid and mid price. Positve number means buying above the mid and selling below the mid.

Name: RejectCost
Description: Cost of rejected trade (in $/m).  Relative move in mid price from the time rejection message was received (time t) to time t + X miliseconds X millisecond can be selected by the used. Side adjusted. Positive number means price goes up after buy and down after sell.

Name: ToxicityOfFills
Description: Relative move in mid price from the time trade was done (time t) to time t + X miliseconds.  X millisecond can be selected by the used. Side adjusted

Name: RejectToFill
Description: Ratio of the RejectedVolume to the FillVolume

Name: VolumeShare
Description: Is the share of total fill volume

Name: RejectCostUSD
Description: Is RejectVolume times RejectCost. It is expressed in USD rather than millions of USD of rejections
